 Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":163,"end_time":401.35,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":400.75,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Do you know why, Tim?","index":164,"end_time":403.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":401.35,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"This one is on you.","index":165,"end_time":404.17,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":403.13,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Because I created the agenda yesterday and on in our Slack chat, you.","index":166,"end_time":409.89,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":404.17,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"You wrote Rusam.","index":167,"end_time":411.25,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":409.89,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So that''s why.","index":168,"end_time":412.21,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":411.41,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":169,"end_time":413.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":412.93,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":170,"end_time":414.57,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":414.13,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So it will be.","index":171,"end_time":415.25,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":414.57,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"It will be.","index":172,"end_time":415.81,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":415.25,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":173,"end_time":416.21,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":415.81,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"It will be Rustam.","index":174,"end_time":417.25,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":416.21,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Got it.","index":175,"end_time":418.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":417.65,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Got it.","index":176,"end_time":418.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":418.09,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"And then Patrick.","index":177,"end_time":420.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":418.49,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Not Patrick, but Pat Sullivan is Going to be the one that I submit after this call.","index":178,"end_time":424.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":420.61,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Okay.","index":179,"end_time":427.33,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":426.69,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Then let''s go back.","index":180,"end_time":432.04,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":429.56,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So, yeah, we have basically the rough cut completed for the.","index":181,"end_time":444.839,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":437.88,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"We agreed on this.","index":182,"end_time":447,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":445.64,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So we.","index":183,"end_time":447.88,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":447.32,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"On this title, Tim.","index":184,"end_time":449.24,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":447.88,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So we''re just gonna combine those two.","index":185,"end_time":452.4,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":449.32,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So it''s going to be expert perspectives from industry leaders, right?","index":186,"end_time":455.8,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":452.4,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"That''s right, Yep.","index":187,"end_time":458.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":457.25,"speaker_name":"Tim Finnigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":188,"end_time":459.45,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":459.01,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"And that''s what I''m doing in the.","index":189,"end_time":460.41,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":459.45,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Office right after this call.","index":190,"end_time":461.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":460.41,"speaker_name":"Tim Finnigan"},{"text":"I''m knocking those out over the next two hours.","index":191,"end_time":464.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":461.89,"speaker_name":"Tim Finnigan"},{"text":"Amazing, Amazing.","index":192,"end_time":466.85,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":465.33,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Thank you.","in