urprise for you too.","index":261,"end_time":701.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":699.84,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Nothing crazy, but yeah, we''ve got a.","index":262,"end_time":706.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":702.56,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Just an end of year recap.","index":263,"end_time":708.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":706.64,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So like your Spotify or Apple 2025 wrapped just some highlights from the year.","index":264,"end_time":715.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":708.72,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, let''s do it.","index":265,"end_time":716.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":715.84,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"I would love to see that.","index":266,"end_time":718,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":716.72,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Yes.","index":267,"end_time":719.28,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":718.8,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Amazing.","index":268,"end_time":720.16,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":719.52,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"I enjoyed creating this one, to be honest.","index":269,"end_time":723.4,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":720.16,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"And you''ll see why at the end.","index":270,"end_time":726.76,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":724.36,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Of course I. I saved the best until the end.","index":271,"end_time":729.8,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":726.76,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So.","index":272,"end_time":731.48,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":731.08,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":273,"end_time":736.44,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":735.96,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So Total published episodes 17 and total downloads are basically so 1,700, which is 102 average downloads.","index":274,"end_time":751.82,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":736.52,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Downloads per episode on.","index":275,"end_time":753.54,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":752.06,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"On average.","index":276,"end_time":754.3,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":753.54,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"But to put this in context, 90% of podcasts actually don''t make it past episode three.","index":277,"end_time":763.18,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":755.1,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So that''s pretty amazing.","index":278,"end_time":765.82,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":763.26,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Wow.","index":279,"end_time":766.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":766.38,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":280,"end_time":767.9,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":767.5,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"And this is like your all time downloads.","index":281,"end_time":770.3,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":767.9,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"And this year notable spikes were in February and May and when Lisa Kopp and Sasha.","index":282,"end_time":779.96,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":772.06,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"I had to check.","index":283,"end_time":781.72,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":780.76,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"I had to because I was like Googling Sasha and then was like, but is this that girl?","index":284,"end_time":788,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":782.12,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Because the first thing that came up was like her climbing stuff and.","index":285,"end_time":792.24,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":788,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":286,"end_time":794.36,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":792.24,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"That''s amazing.","index":287,"end_time":795.16,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":794.36,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah, she just became the first.","index":288,"end_time":797.4,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":795.32,"speaker_name":"Tim Finnigan"},{"text":"She just accomplished.","index":289,"end_time":798.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":797.48,"speaker_name":"Tim Finnigan"},{"text":"She''s the first woman to climb El Capitan.","index":290,"end_time":801.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":798.76,"speaker_name":"Tim Finnigan"},{"text":"Oh man.","index":291,"end_time":802.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":802.13,"speaker_name":"Tim Finnigan"},{"text":"Can we post about that and just share some clips?","index":292,"end_time":805.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":803.01,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Instagram.","index":293,"end_time":806.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":805.89,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"You should have seen like she''s in a tent on the side of a mountain like waiting for a storm together.","index":294,"end_time":812.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":806.45,"speaker_name":"Tim Finnigan"},{"text":"It''s like she was there for like I think a month and there was like a week and a half of storms.","index":295,"end_time":816.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":812.29,"speaker_name":"Tim Finnigan"},{"text":"That''s insane.","index":296,"end_time":818.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":817.73,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Crazy.","index":297,"end_time":820.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":819.41,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"That''s really crazy.","index":298,"end_time":821.41,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":820.21,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":299,"end_time":821.89,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":821.41,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"And then regarding your audience demographics, most of them are in North America and then Europe and Asia are second and third place and then iPhone and Apple Podcasts.","index":300,"end_time":843.62,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":826.21,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So 65 and 55%.","index":301,"end_time":845.9,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":843.62,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"And this is, this was really interesting to me.","i