id":0,"start_time":1023.79,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"As we start posting more shorts, that number is going to go up a lot as well.","index":359,"end_time":1030.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1025.87,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s just what I''m seeing.","index":360,"end_time":1031.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1030.67,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"For our other clients, this is my viewing.","index":361,"end_time":1034.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1031.83,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"It''s TMR podcast on YouTube.","index":362,"end_time":1037.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1034.67,"speaker_name":"Tim Finnigan"},{"text":"Then the real Housewives of Salt Lake City.","index":363,"end_time":1039.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1037.31,"speaker_name":"Tim Finnigan"},{"text":"Yes.","index":364,"end_time":1042.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1041.47,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Love island.","index":365,"end_time":1043.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1042.66,"speaker_name":"Tim Finnigan"},{"text":"And then.","index":366,"end_time":1044.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1044.02,"speaker_name":"Tim Finnigan"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":367,"end_time":1047.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1046.58,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Everyone just wants to learn at least like.","index":368,"end_time":1050.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1047.7,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I get that too.","index":369,"end_time":1051.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1050.66,"speaker_name":"Tim Finnigan"},{"text":"She''s like that.","index":370,"end_time":1052.42,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1051.82,"speaker_name":"Tim Finnigan"},{"text":"That''s.","index":371,"end_time":1052.9,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1052.42,"speaker_name":"Tim Finnigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":372,"end_time":1053.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1053.38,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Who wants to watch trashy TV when we can learn how to be marketers.","index":373,"end_time":1058.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1053.78,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, maybe, maybe you could sell it to Netflix or something like that.","index":374,"end_time":1065.06,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1061.22,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Right?","index":375,"end_time":1065.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1065.54,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"I think so.","index":376,"end_time":1067.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1066.5,"speaker_name":"Tim Finnigan"},{"text":"And then.","index":377,"end_time":1069.63,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1069.15,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Tada.","index":378,"end_time":1071.15,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1070.51,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"These are actually.","index":379,"end_time":1072.67,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1071.31,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":380,"end_time":1073.07,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1072.67,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"The recognitions and rankings for this year, so.","index":381,"end_time":1076.19,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1073.07,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":382,"end_time":1077.39,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1076.91,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"I didn''t even know we were mentioned.","index":383,"end_time":1079.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1078.03,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":384,"end_time":1081.87,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1080.91,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Number two on their list of 15 best data driven marketing podcasts and number 71 on their list of 100 best marketing podcasts.","index":385,"end_time":1092.03,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1081.87,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Where do you get this from?","index":386,"end_time":1093.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1092.27,"speaker_name":"Tim Finnigan"},{"text":"Beads?","index":387,"end_time":1095.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":