,"end_time":1159.14,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1158.74,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"I Wonder like in 26 because we''re gonna start re engaging PR activities.","index":419,"end_time":1163.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1159.14,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"So like obviously not just like our podcast, but trying to get Tim on other podcasts as well.","index":420,"end_time":1170.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1163.78,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"And I''m hoping that maybe we can get more placements like this through a PR person or an agency, whatever we decide to do.","index":421,"end_time":1180.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1172.02,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"So that''s really awesome.","index":422,"end_time":1182.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1180.99,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"I''m really proud of us.","index":423,"end_time":1183.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1182.59,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Go team.","index":424,"end_time":1184.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1183.63,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"You didn''t even know.","index":425,"end_time":1186.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1185.07,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"It doesn''t even happening.","index":426,"end_time":1188.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1186.43,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":427,"end_time":1189.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1188.51,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":428,"end_time":1191.55,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1191.15,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Amazing.","index":429,"end_time":1192.03,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1191.55,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Amazing.","index":430,"end_time":1192.75,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1192.19,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah, I, that, yeah, I really enjoyed it.","index":431,"end_time":1195.07,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1192.75,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Like especially the, the last part where I actually saw that.","index":432,