idn''t realize I was looking on Spotify and I was looking at Apple and Spotify.","index":447,"end_time":1234.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1228.72,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"It''s very clear.","index":448,"end_time":1235,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1234.24,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Like we are a five star podcast based on like 17 reviews or something like that.","index":449,"end_time":1241.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1235,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"I commented on an episode.","index":450,"end_time":1243.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1242.08,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"I want to get more into commenting on episodes on Spotify next year.","index":451,"end_time":1247.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1243.88,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"I feel like it''s good engagement but yeah, this is, that is interesting that we are number two on this list.","index":452,"end_time":1256.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1247.76,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"That''s great.","index":453,"end_time":1257.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1257.28,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Yay.","index":454,"end_time":1258.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1258,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Oh, there''s 14 Apple reviews.","index":455,"end_time":1261.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1259.45,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Yay.","index":456,"end_time":1262.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1261.61,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"I''m learning so much.","index":457,"end_time":1265.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1264.25,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Cool.","index":458,"end_time":1267.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1266.81,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":459,"end_time":1269.09,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1268.65,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Go Varisk.","index":460,"end_time":1270.01,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1269.09,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Great.","index":461,"end_time":1272.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1272.25,"speaker_name":"Gab"},{"text":"Lots o