  '[{"text":"Provide New North team with a comprehensive Summit brief covering event overview, messaging, sessions, and post-event content strategy (16:06)","completed":false},{"text":"Own briefing process and coordinate sharing of detailed content packages with New North for informed content creation (16:06)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide event slide decks and descriptions of speakers in more detail to New North as available (18:13)","completed":false},{"text":"Pull video recordings post-event and share with New North (17:44)","completed":false},{"text":"Determine preferred deliverables and timeline with New North based on briefing and content from the event (28:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Register New North team for the Summit event to enable their attendance (29:18)","completed":false},{"text":"Create templates for quote cards and promotional ads ahead of Summit event for faster post-event delivery (09:42)","completed":false},{"text":"Develop recommended content deliverables and proposed timeline after finalizing Summit materials (27:46)","completed":false},{"text":"Collaborate with Bazaar Voice on leveraging Boldcast AI clipping functionality for post-event video assets if given access (18:01)","completed":false},{"text":"Align with Bazaar Voice team on the preferred structure and bundling of post-event content to maintain consistency (08:07)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate sharing of Canva design templates to facilitate asset production with New North (28:40)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
