-- Meeting: iCorps + New North Weekly Meeting (2025-12-10 15:30:00+00)
WITH new_meeting AS (
  INSERT INTO compass_meetings (contract_id, meeting_date, source, external_id, title, participants, duration_seconds, recording_url, transcript, sentiment, raw_metadata, created_at, updated_at)
  VALUES (
    '965b21f3-8748-420c-aaf3-b3fdcaa2f504',
    '2025-12-10 15:30:00+00',
    'fireflies',
    '01KBZS8HBPQ32HYKGX2Q251MB5',
    'iCorps + New North Weekly Meeting',
    '{"Samuel Bagnall","Ruby Pontbriand","Nathalie Mintjens"}'::text[],
    409,
    'https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meetup-join/19:meeting_MDUyZTNiYTMtMTMxNi00YWUyLWI0MjktZjNiZjI1NWU5MGMy@thread.v2/0?context={"Tid":"0188564a-93de-489c-bf54-1927d4a9ed28","Oid":"bdae9fd3-d481-4c5e-aeea-7272e37b7d07"}',
    '{"id":"01KBZS8HBPQ32HYKGX2Q251MB5","title":"iCorps + New North Weekly Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Account-Based Marketing (ABM) Campaign Execution**\n\nThe ABM campaign has launched with multiple outreach channels now actively engaging targeted leads to drive legal services growth.\n\n- **The AI-driven campaign began sending emails and LinkedIn connection requests, with Kristen assigned to follow up on responses** (02:15)  \n    - LinkedIn messages and emails are linked to a highly engaged lead list for precise targeting  \n    - Kristen will monitor LinkedIn several times daily and the campaign email inbox for replies  \n    - Automated assignment ensures timely follow-up on all engaged prospects  \n    - This approach aims to boost lead conversion rates by personalizing outreach based on engagement tracking  \n\n- **LinkedIn ads for the campaign are scheduled to launch tomorrow, with updated forms requiring business emails instead of auto-filled personal data** (02:46)  \n    - This change is designed to improve lead quality and data accuracy  \n    - The new form format aligns with privacy standards and reduces invalid leads  \n    - Nathalie emphasized this as a key step to enhance campaign effectiveness and compliance  \n\n- **An analytics dashboard has been set up to track campaign performance weekly across LinkedIn and email metrics** (03:05)  \n    - Metrics include connection requests sent and accepted, messages sent and replied to, email opens, clicks, and replies  \n    - This real-time visibility will allow the team to quickly adapt messaging and targeting tactics  \n    - Ruby confirmed the dashboard facilitates ongoing measurement and optimization of outreach efforts  \n\n## **SEO Content Update and Review**\n\nSEO content updates for key location pages are advancing with refined messaging and alignment to service offerings.\n\n- **Revised SEO pages incorporating Jeff’s requested bullet points and new service blurbs have been completed for the Boston page** (03:52)  \n    - Other location pages have updated blurbs but use card layouts instead of bullets to match design differences  \n    - Nathalie will send these pages back to Jeff for final review and approval  \n    - Ruby confirmed the content updates meet expectations and enhance service clarity for local search relevance  \n    - This aims to improve organic traffic and lead capture by better aligning content to user intent  \n\n- **Pages currently under review will await Jeff’s feedback before moving forward** (04:55)  \n    - Nathalie plans to consolidate all SEO pages and send a comprehensive update to Samuel post-meeting  \n    - This ensures all stakeholders have access to the latest versions and can provide timely input  \n    - Samuel emphasized the need for easy access to these pages to stay aligned during his return from vacation  \n\n## **Team Coordination and Communication**\n\nThe team is focusing on clear communication channels and resource alignment to support campaign execution and content delivery.\n\n- **Kristen’s role is clarified as the primary point for LinkedIn and email follow-ups on the ABM campaign** (02:15)  \n    - This centralizes accountability and ensures no leads fall through the cracks  \n    - Nathalie’s coordination of campaign tracking and updates supports Kristen’s workflow  \n\n- **Samuel requested consolidated access to all updated SEO pages to catch up quickly after vacation** (05:20)  \n    - Nathalie committed to emailing all current and revised SEO content immediately after the meeting  \n    - Ruby and Nathalie’s support helps reduce onboarding friction and keeps Samuel fully informed  \n\n- **The upcoming company holiday party is scheduled for Saturday, with Samuel and Ruby leading its organization** (05:48)  \n    - This signals a temporary shift in team focus but also an opportunity for informal bonding  \n    - Samuel expressed relief that post-event planning workload will ease, allowing refocus on work priorities  \n\n## **Process Enhancements and Monitoring**\n\nThe team is implementing new processes and tools to improve outreach quality and campaign oversight.\n\n- **Switching LinkedIn lead forms to require manual business email entry enhances lead data quality and reduces errors** (02:46)  \n    - This process change addresses previous issues with inaccurate or incomplete contact info  \n    - It also aligns with stricter data privacy and marketing compliance standards  \n\n- **The weekly analytics dashboard provides a structured framework for monitoring campaign KPIs and guiding rapid adjustments** (03:05)  \n    - This supports agile marketing by identifying what works and where to pivot quickly  \n    - The dashboard covers multi-channel engagement metrics to give a complete performance view  \n\n- **Automated lead assignment to Kristen ensures faster response times and better lead nurturing** (02:15)  \n    - This system reduces manual handoff delays and minimizes lost follow-up opportunities  \n    - It builds accountability into the campaign workflow  \n\n- **SEO content review workflow involves iterative feedback loops with Jeff to ensure alignment and quality before publishing** (03:52)  \n    - This minimizes errors and ensures messaging consistency across location pages  \n    - It helps maintain brand voice and improves SEO impact through strategic content placement","outline":null,"keywords":["AI campaign","LinkedIn ads","SEO updates","analytics dashboard","ABM campaign","holiday party planning"],"overview":"- **ABM Campaign Launch:** Multiple outreach channels active; personalized follow-up aims to boost lead conversion rates.\n\n- **LinkedIn Ads Update:** Ads launching tomorrow with new forms requiring business emails to improve lead quality.\n\n- **Analytics Dashboard Set Up:** Weekly tracking for LinkedIn and email metrics facilitates quick adjustments and optimization.\n\n- **SEO Content Updates:** Boston page revised with new service blurbs; feedback from Jeff is pending for other location pages.\n\n- **Team Coordination:** Clear roles established for Kristen and Nathalie to maintain communication and resource alignment.\n\n- **Upcoming Company Event:** Holiday party set for Saturday; focus shifts temporarily, allowing for team bonding opportunities.","action_items":"\n**Kristen**\nMonitor LinkedIn connection requests and respond to any incoming messages daily (01:18)\nFollow up on highly engaged lead list contacts automatically assigned from the campaign (02:20)\n\n**Nathalie Mintjens**\nSend updated SEO pages and related documents to Samuel for review and reference post-meeting (05:29)\n\n**Samuel Bagnall**\nReview the SEO pages Nathalie will provide and follow up with Jeff or Nathalie as needed (05:20)\n"},"duration":6.820000171661377,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"id":1,"name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"id":2,"name":"Nathalie Mintjens"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Hey Adeline, how you doing?","index":0,"end_time":6.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":4.96,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Hey.","index":1,"end_time":7.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":7.12,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Good.","index":2,"end_time":8.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":8.24,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"How was your vacation?","index":3,"end_time":9.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":8.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It was good.","index":4,"end_time":11.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":10.56,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"It''s a ton of fun, but I''m just getting back to it.","index":5,"end_time":15.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":12.8,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":6,"end_time":17.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":16.72,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Did you get back on Monday?","index":7,"end_time":18.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":17.12,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, Monday night at like nine something.","index":8,"end_time":22.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":19.2,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":9,"end_time":24.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":23.2,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I was back home by the way, so I wasn''t, wasn''t too bad.","index":10,"end_time":27.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":24.88,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":11,"end_time":28.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":28.39,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Gone back later.","index":12,"end_time":29.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":28.87,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Before.","index":13,"end_time":29.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":29.55,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Was it warm in Mexico?","index":14,"end_time":33.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":31.91,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It was like in the 70s.","index":15,"end_time":36.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":35.43,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Okay.","index":16,"end_time":38.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":37.59,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":17,"end_time":39.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":38.63,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"So that was a good.","index":18,"end_time":40.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":39.27,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Not too hot.","index":19,"end_time":41.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":40.31,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"It did rain one of the days, but yeah, other than that it was really nice.","index":20,"end_time":46.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":42.63,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Nice.","index":21,"end_time":47.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":47.27,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"What''s your weather like?","index":22,"end_time":48.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":47.91,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Is it freezing?","index":23,"end_time":49.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":48.83,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"It''s been like non stop snowing for like two weeks.","index":24,"end_time":53.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":51.03,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh yeah?","index":25,"end_time":55.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":53.83,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":26,"end_time":56.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":55.78,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Well, it was like 23 here yesterday.","index":27,"end_time":59.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":56.58,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"2623.","index":28,"end_time":60.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":59.7,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"So it was cold.","index":29,"end_time":62.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":61.7,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Didn''t snow though.","index":30,"end_time":63.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":62.58,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I just know I was gone.","index":31,"end_time":65.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":64.58,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I don''t know, but I think it did.","index":32,"end_time":67.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":65.82,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Hey, Ruby.","index":33,"end_time":71.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":70.9,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Hey guys.","index":34,"end_time":73.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":72.9,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"How''s it going?","index":35,"end_time":74.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":73.54,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Good, good.","index":36,"end_time":75.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":74.34,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"How are you?","index":37,"end_time":76.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":76.1,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Good, I''m good.","index":38,"end_time":78.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":76.78,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Just juggling a sick kid.","index":39,"end_time":80.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":79.38,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Oh no.","index":40,"end_time":82.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":81.7,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"All right.","index":41,"end_time":84.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":83.99,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It''s the season.","index":42,"end_time":85.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":84.31,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":43,"end_time":86.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":85.59,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"All right.","index":44,"end_time":87.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":86.87,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So a couple of updates today.","index":45,"end_time":92.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":90.23,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, so I sent the note a couple of days ago that the AI campaign launched, so that''s awesome.","index":46,"end_time":114.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":105.11,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we have the emails going out as well as the LinkedIn messages as well.","index":47,"end_time":119.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":114.87,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So just a note to Kristin that those, those connection requests have started sending.","index":48,"end_time":126.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":120.47,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So she should just be looking at her LinkedIn maybe a couple times a day seeing if any responses do come in.","index":49,"end_time":132.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":126.31,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then we''ll also be monitoring the email inbox as well to see if any responses come come in.","index":50,"end_time":138.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":133.35,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then we''ve connected the campaign to the highly engaged lead list.","index":51,"end_time":144.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":139.53,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So as we''re tracking people''s activity, we''ll start to see their names populating here and then we''ll make sure that they are tied to the legal services ABM campaign and they''re all going to be automatically assigned to Kristen as well for follow up.","index":52,"end_time":161.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":145.13,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, awesome.","index":53,"end_time":163.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":162.65,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And Then for the LinkedIn ads for this campaign.","index":54,"end_time":168.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":166.07,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So those will launch tomorrow.","index":55,"end_time":170.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":168.15,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then we did change all of the forms on LinkedIn so they''re now they''re not going to auto populate with the contact''s personal LinkedIn account.","index":56,"end_time":179.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":171.11,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Instead it''s going to ask them to type in a business email.","index":57,"end_time":183.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":180.23,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Perfect, thank you.","index":58,"end_time":185.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":183.75,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":59,"end_time":186.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":185.75,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then lastly we have this analytics dashboard just to look at this campaign as it starts to send out.","index":60,"end_time":195.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":187.99,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we''ll be able to see LinkedIn connection requests that are sent, how many connection requests were accepted, then the messages sent and then the replies and then same for email, how many have been sent, opened and Clicked and then replied as well.","index":61,"end_time":211.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":195.4,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we''ll be able to look at this on a weekly basis, see how we''re tracking.","index":62,"end_time":215.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":211.96,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":63,"end_time":217.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":216.53,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":64,"end_time":219.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":219.41,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Anything?","index":65,"end_time":222.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":221.73,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Any other questions about the ABM campaign?","index":66,"end_time":224.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":222.25,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Nope, I think we''re good.","index":67,"end_time":227.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":226.53,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Great.","index":68,"end_time":229.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":228.85,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"And then for SEO.","index":69,"end_time":234.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":232.45,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So I. I took back the pages that we had sent over to Jeff.","index":70,"end_time":239.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":234.69,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then just wanted to show you what we''ve done.","index":71,"end_time":243.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":241.66,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So.","index":72,"end_time":244.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":244.38,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"This is what he asked for, I believe, is, like, having all of these different bullet points.","index":73,"end_time":251.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":246.94,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"These ones on the left, these ones on the right.","index":74,"end_time":253.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":251.1,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then he also sent over a new introductory blurb about the services.","index":75,"end_time":259.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":253.9,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we''ve added that over here.","index":76,"end_time":260.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":259.18,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And this is for the Boston page.","index":77,"end_time":264.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":262.54,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"The other two pages are a little bit different because we don''t have the bullet points.","index":78,"end_time":268.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":264.38,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We instead have these cards.","index":79,"end_time":271.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":269.41,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But we did add in the blurb that he sent over over here and then just change the location.","index":80,"end_time":281.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":273.89,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So I''ll send these back over to you for him to check, see if there''s anything else he''d like us to adjust.","index":81,"end_time":287.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":281.65,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Cool.","index":82,"end_time":290.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":289.89,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"They look good.","index":83,"end_time":291.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":290.33,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":84,"end_time":291.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":291.09,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":85,"end_time":292.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":292.13,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":86,"end_time":294.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":294.54,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Okay, I''ll send those over.","index":87,"end_time":297.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":295.18,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then.","index":88,"end_time":297.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":297.34,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"You guys still have these ones in review as well, so we''ll just wait until Jeff has a chance to look at those.","index":89,"end_time":306.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":299.74,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"All right.","index":90,"end_time":310.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":310.3,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"That was everything I had.","index":91,"end_time":313.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":311.98,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So, anything else you wanted to discuss?","index":92,"end_time":315.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":314.06,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I guess just.","index":93,"end_time":321.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":320.55,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Where can I find those pages?","index":94,"end_time":324.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":323.03,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Are they in the.","index":95,"end_time":326.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":325.27,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":96,"end_time":326.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":326.63,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Are they in our, like, portal?","index":97,"end_time":328.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":326.99,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah, I could also.","index":98,"end_time":330.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":329.51,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''ll just send an email after this.","index":99,"end_time":331.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":330.43,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":100,"end_time":332.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":331.99,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Sorry.","index":101,"end_time":332.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":332.43,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m just trying to, like, catch back up.","index":102,"end_time":334.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":332.87,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah, I know it''s a lot.","index":103,"end_time":336.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":334.71,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll just.","index":104,"end_time":336.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":336.39,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''ll gather all of them and then send them over.","index":105,"end_time":338.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":336.99,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, thank you.","index":106,"end_time":339.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":338.87,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah, sure.","index":107,"end_time":340.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":339.67,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":108,"end_time":342.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":341.59,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":109,"end_time":342.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":342.23,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Of course.","index":110,"end_time":344.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":343.75,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Are you looking forward to the holidays?","index":111,"end_time":347.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":345.84,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":112,"end_time":349.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":348.8,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Holiday party is on Saturday, so.","index":113,"end_time":351.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":349.44,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":114,"end_time":353.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":352.88,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah, it''ll be good.","index":115,"end_time":354.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":353.52,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Are you guys in charge of organizing it?","index":116,"end_time":359.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":356.48,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yes.","index":117,"end_time":360.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":360.08,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":118,"end_time":361.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":360.72,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Sure.","index":119,"end_time":363.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":362.8,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbrian