  VALUES (
    '4995ddd4-5ee9-4673-9a9b-c773e431992a',
    '2025-12-11 13:30:00+00',
    'fireflies',
    '01KBMWGFRMW60WZQ8VTV4ANJ7G',
    'Agrippon // New North Weekly Connect',
    '{"Shane Billings","Keenan Toward","Shane Billings","Nathalie Mintjens"}'::text[],
    1300,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/83663022990?pwd=R1aTMdTGv2yblYfzlB6Wv1Sup4Z47U.1',
    '{"id":"01KBMWGFRMW60WZQ8VTV4ANJ7G","title":"Agrippon // New North Weekly Connect","summary":{"notes":"## **Marketing Campaign Performance and Budget Management**\n\nThe team paused the **LinkedIn ad campaigns** due to a sharp increase in **cost per click rising over three to four times** the initial rate, prompting a detailed review and adjustment plan (01:29).  \n- Nathalie Mintjens will collaborate with the paid media specialist to diagnose causes and propose recommendations next week.  \n- Shane Billings emphasized setting a clear **cost per click target around $4–5** to control spending.  \n- The increase is linked to a narrowed audience focused on re-engaging previously involved users, which naturally drives up costs.  \n- The goal is to optimize spend while maintaining engagement to avoid budget overruns and ineffective campaigns.\n\nRestarting **LinkedIn outreach messages under Keenan Toward’s account** was approved to boost engagement over paused channels (02:36).  \n- Nathalie explained the use of Heyreach to automate messages without compromising account privacy.  \n- Keenan raised concerns about managing multiple LinkedIn accounts due to platform restrictions; Shane confirmed LinkedIn flags multiple accounts, so they will proceed carefully.  \n- This move aims to leverage higher response rates from LinkedIn messages versus emails, increasing lead quality and volume.\n\nConcerns about **account point usage showed a purchase of 350 points but delivery of 850 points**, creating a significant debt and raising budget control alarms (14:41).  \n- Shane expressed worry about accumulating unmanageable debt, stressing the need to balance experimentation with financial limits.  \n- Nathalie acknowledged ongoing ramp-up and experimentation but committed to consulting with Colin to clarify and manage point usage and budget pacing.  \n- Keenan confirmed the **350 points purchased is cumulative**, while the monthly purchase is **50 points**, highlighting the need to monitor usage closely.  \n- This financial oversight is critical to ensuring sustainable marketing spend and avoiding unexpected costs.\n\n## **Website and Lead Management Enhancements**\n\nThe **website’s calendly links were removed and replaced by forms**, causing confusion for leads, but all related website updates including calendar link restoration are scheduled to be completed today (05:12).  \n- Nathalie confirmed developers will finalize these changes and send a pull request for Shane to launch after review.  \n- A recent lead experienced scheduling confusion due to the broken links, underscoring the urgency of restoring smooth booking flows.  \n- Submitted forms now feed directly into Zoho CRM, improving lead capture accuracy and tracking.  \n- Reinstating calendly links aims to provide multiple meeting types, including demos and needs consultations, enhancing lead qualification.\n\nKeenan and Shane agreed to review and approve **website text and design changes** before publishing, targeting feedback by **Monday** to ensure smooth rollout (20:24).  \n- Nathalie has the changes ready and will send design files immediately after the meeting for review.  \n- Keenan is dedicating focused time to Grippon projects to expedite this process and ensure quality control.  \n- This step aims to refresh the website experience while maintaining alignment with lead generation goals.\n\nA weekly report on **company visitors to the Agrippon website** was introduced, highlighting key accounts with visit frequency and recent activity (07:17).  \n- Nathalie prioritized the most relevant accounts and included details like page views and first pages visited.  \n- Shane requested clarifications on visitor counts and email clicks to better understand lead sources.  \n- This report will be sent weekly to Shane and Keenan to support targeted outreach and conversion efforts.  \n- Tracking repeat visitors and ABM traffic, which rose by **53%,** provides valuable insights into campaign effectiveness.\n\n## **Traffic and Engagement Metrics Analysis**\n\nOverall website traffic shows **steady growth** with **visitors up 8%** and **page views up 4%** over the last 30 days, signaling improving user interest (10:03).  \n- The **case study page''s traffic surged by 53%**, indicating strong content engagement in this area.  \n- Direct traffic increased by **9%**, reflecting growing repeat visits and link sharing, key for organic growth.  \n- ABM-related traffic, including emails and LinkedIn, also rose by **53%**, validating current outreach methods.  \n- Conversely, the contact page saw a slight decline, prompting consideration of whether new meeting options will reverse this trend.\n\nKeenan recommended **not making immediate changes to the case study page**, preferring to first implement the planned facelift across the website and LinkedIn to assess overall impact (11:36).  \n- He emphasized cleaning up old LinkedIn content to present a refreshed brand image before further adjustments.  \n- This cautious approach aims to avoid disruptive changes while optimizing lead funnel quality.  \n- Observations from recent leads indicate the current setup is generating activity, supporting the decision to maintain the course for now.\n\n## **Account and System Access Coordination**\n\nShane holds the **billing organization lead role** with near-full platform access, enabling him to assist Keenan with demo environment setup and account management (13:51).  \n- Keenan will coordinate with Shane for any technical configurations or ticket requests related to demos and office system changes.  \n- Shane receives periodic emails summarizing account point usage, which he uses to monitor consumption and financial status.  \n- There is a need to resolve Shane’s locked access to the Pulse portal, with Nathalie planning to coordinate with Colin to restore permissions promptly (18:50).  \n- Improved access will enhance Shane’s ability to track metrics and guide marketing decisions efficiently.\n\n## **Content and Social Media Strategy**\n\nSocial media posts for **December**, combining educational podcast content and direct product promotion, were prepared and sent for review (06:44).  \n- Keenan plans to review the content promptly to provide feedback and ensure alignment with overall messaging.  \n- This blend aims to educate potential customers while encouraging meeting bookings, supporting lead nurturing efforts.  \n- Effective social media presence supports the broader ABM strategy that has already shown positive traffic results.\n\n## **Process and Communication Enhancements**\n\nThe team agreed on **weekly reporting cadence** for visitor data and campaign performance to maintain transparency and timely adjustments (09:35).  \n- Nathalie will send these reports directly to Shane and Keenan to keep key stakeholders informed.  \n- Shane requested email notifications for pull requests to allow prompt review and deployment, ensuring smooth coordination with developers.  \n- Clear communication protocols around campaign goals, budget usage, and content approvals were emphasized to align efforts and avoid missteps.  \n- This structured approach aims to improve operational efficiency and accountability across marketing and product teams.","outline":null,"keywords":["LinkedIn outreach","cost per click","website updates","calendly integration","lead management","billing points"],"overview":"- **LinkedIn Ad Campaigns:** Paused due to cost per click rising 3-4 times; new target set at $4–5 per click.  \n- **Messaging Strategy:** Restart of LinkedIn outreach metrics expected to increase lead quality; automation via Heyreach for efficiency.  \n- **Point Usage Concerns:** 350 points purchased vs. 850 delivered; need to manage budget pacing and usage closely.  \n- **Website Updates:** Calendar links restored; forms now integrated with Zoho CRM for better lead tracking and booking.  \n- **Traffic Growth:** Website visitors up 8% and ABM traffic increased 53%; case study page engagement notably strong.  \n- **Weekly Reports:** Established for visitor data and campaign performance to enhance transparency and guide marketing decisions.","action_items":"\n**Nathalie Mintjens**\nWork with paid media specialist to diagnose LinkedIn ad campaigns and provide recommendations to control CPC, send update next week (02:33)\nSend instructions to Keenan to set up Heyreach for LinkedIn automated messages outbound from his account (03:02)\nComplete website updates including calendly link re-addition today, and notify Shane with the pull request for launching (05:18)\nAdd email click data to website visitor report and send the weekly visitor list to Shane and Keenan (09:31)\nConfer with Colin regarding the billing points overspend and report back to Shane (16:36)\nCoordinate with Colin to resolve Shane’s locked access to the Pulse portal (19:30)\nSend Keenan the website design file for text and calendly changes immediately after the meeting for review prior to publishing (21:11)\n\n**Keenan Toward**\nReview December social media posts and provide feedback promptly (06:58)\nAssess LinkedIn account setup regarding messaging and dual account risks (03:31)\nReview website visitor report and monitor lead sources with Shane (09:35)\nReview website design files once received; provide updated feedback by Monday to progress to live implementation (21:03)\nReschedule and manage leads emerging from website/email outreach, including a lead initially associated with Monique (06:28)\n\n**Shane Billings**\nAwait the pull request from Nathalie for website text and calendly updates, then review for conflicts and launch (09:56)\nProvide access or share screenshots relating to the Pulse portal issue with Nathalie to assist in troubleshooting (18:56)\n"},"duration":21.670000076293945,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Shane Billings"},{"id":1,"name":"Keenan Toward"},{"id":2,"name":"Shane Billings"},{"id":3,"name":"Nathalie Mintjens"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Hey, Keenan.","index":0,"end_time":1.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.4,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Good morning.","index":1,"end_time":5.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":4.32,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"How are you?","index":2,"end_time":6.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":5.84,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Not too bad.","index":3,"end_time":8.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":7.2,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"How about you?","index":4,"end_time":10.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":9.92,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I''m hanging in there.","index":5,"end_time":12.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":11.44,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Good.","index":6,"end_time":13.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":13.2,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":7,"end_time":15.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":15.44,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So for today''s agenda, we''ll go through what you have.","index":8,"end_time":21.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":18.24,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Natalie.","index":9,"end_time":21.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":21.28,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I also want to really make sure we cover progress towards the software, the soft launch that we''re hoping for in December, and then we can talk about.","index":10,"end_time":33.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":21.88,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Like.","index":11,"end_time":34.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":33.81,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I want to know how we are.","index":12,"end_time":40.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":37.33,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Like, charged.","index":13,"end_time":45.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":43.97,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I want to know a little bit more about that.","index":14,"end_time":47.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":45.89,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I think I get emails from you, but I want to know where we stand in our account.","index":15,"end_time":52.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":47.65,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay, yeah, we can go over that.","index":16,"end_time":55.96,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":53.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Right.","index":17,"end_time":62.52,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":62.12,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So for our agenda for the LinkedIn ad chain, just like the email said, I did pause those campaigns just for the time being.","index":18,"end_time":76.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":68.52,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And I''m going to work with our paid media specialist just to go into what we have running and diagnose it, see why the cost per click went up, and then come back with a few recommendations.","index":19,"end_time":88.49,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":77.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, it''s not a small amount.","index":20,"end_time":91.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":89.13,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"It''s over three, four times as much.","index":21,"end_time":93.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":91.17,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So, yeah, it''s huge.","index":22,"end_time":95.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":93.93,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Huge jump.","index":23,"end_time":96.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":96.01,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":24,"end_time":98.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":97.53,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":25,"end_time":99.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":98.809,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":26,"end_time":102.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":101.69,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then I''ll.","index":27,"end_time":102.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":102.09,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''ll send those over to you once I have them, and then I could, could I.","index":28,"end_time":106.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":102.53,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Could I ask you to set a goal to keep those at a certain amount?","index":29,"end_time":110.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":106.89,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, Like, I think you guys should have a target that you''re trying to achieve.","index":30,"end_time":117.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":111.94,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":31,"end_time":118.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":118.02,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll work with them to see what''s best there.","index":32,"end_time":125.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":121.7,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, it started out around 4, 5.","index":33,"end_time":127.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":125.78,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":34,"end_time":130.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":129.78,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And so.","index":35,"end_time":131.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":130.26,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I think my, I mean, my first thought is that because we changed the audience, we''re using part of our budget, if you remember, to re.","index":36,"end_time":142.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":133.3,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Engage people that had some engagement.","index":37,"end_time":144.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":142.05,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So it''s a much smaller list of people, which is why I think the cost per click is going up.","index":38,"end_time":149.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":144.69,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But yeah, I''ll come back to you next week with some ideas.","index":39,"end_time":153.49,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":149.81,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":40,"end_time":154.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":153.89,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":41,"end_time":156.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":156.05,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then for LinkedIn outreach, I wanted to check if we should start changing all of the outreach to come from Keenan.","index":42,"end_time":164.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":157.09,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Now, in the past, the, like, the LinkedIn messages were always got much higher engagement than emails, but they''re all paused right now.","index":43,"end_time":172.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":164.08,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So I think we should start them again.","index":44,"end_time":174,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":172.48,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And we can set them up through Keenan, if that''s okay.","index":45,"end_time":178.4,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":175.6,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, I think that''s best.","index":46,"end_time":181.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":180.32,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Okay.","index":47,"end_time":183.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":182.72,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, so I''ll send you.","index":48,"end_time":189.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":188.65,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''ll send you some instructions.","index":49,"end_time":191.73,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":190.41,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Keenan.","index":50,"end_time":192.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":191.73,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We use a tool called Heyreach, which would just connect to your LinkedIn account and it would allow us to send out those automated messages.","index":51,"end_time":199.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":192.21,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And it, it doesn''t give us any access to view your LinkedIn account.","index":52,"end_time":205.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":202.009,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It just lets us send those outbound messages.","index":53,"end_time":208.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":206.41,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"O.","index":54,"end_time":211.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":210.73,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":55,"end_time":211.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":211.13,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"This.","index":56,"end_time":212.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":211.65,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I guess two questions.","index":57,"end_time":214.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":213.89,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Does the.","index":58,"end_time":215.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":214.85,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Person receiving it see my account?","index":59,"end_time":219.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":217.01,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So do I need to change what my current account looks like?","index":60,"end_time":222.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":219.49,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Because I''m working two roles essentially.","index":61,"end_time":227.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":223.97,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So if I go and change everything to, say, a grip on or I guess maybe I have a different account, is there a way I haven''t used LinkedIn enough?","index":62,"end_time":236.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":228.13,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"LinkedIn will flag you if you.","index":63,"end_time":239.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":237.09,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"It doesn''t like two accounts.","index":64,"end_time":241.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":239.49,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"If it''s.","index":65,"end_time":241.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":241.01,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"If it thinks and it does pretty good job of finding those things and shutting you down.","index":66,"end_time":247.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":241.57,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So you.","index":67,"end_time":247.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":247.28,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"What would.","index":68,"end_time":248.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":247.72,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I''ve experienced this where you create two accounts trying to attack two different sides of things.","index":69,"end_time":253.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":248.56,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"If they find out, they just shut one down.","index":70,"end_time":255.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":253.6,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":71,"end_time":256.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":256.4,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay, I''ll take a look at that today, though.","index":72,"end_time":259.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":257.52,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"But yeah, if you''ll send that over, Natalie.","index":73,"end_time":262.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":259.56,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And then kind of on that same note, the calendly links that were on the website before, when I click there now those are gone.","index":74,"end_time":269.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":262.04,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Right.","index":75,"end_time":269.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":269.28,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So those are not active.","index":76,"end_time":271.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":270.15,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yeah, you should be seeing forms now.","index":77,"end_time":274.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":272.39,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, so I saw forms which, which I, I think is good for the time being.","index":78,"end_time":281.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":275.11,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"We''re going to adjust those to mine, right?","index":79,"end_time":283.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":281.51,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":80,"end_time":284.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":283.75,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we actually had a lead yesterday.","index":81,"end_time":287.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":284.79,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So a woman called to confirm that.","index":82,"end_time":290.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":287.67,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"The one that she scheduled with Monique was still on.","index":83,"end_time":296.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":292.63,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And I was like, oh, when did you schedule it?","index":84,"end_time":301,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":297.84,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"She said, well, about a week ago, but the link doesn''t work anymore for me to confirm it.","index":85,"end_time":305.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":301,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And so, yeah, I just want to make sure we''re in the process.","index":86,"end_time":310.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":306.8,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"What''s the timeline on that?","index":87,"end_time":312.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":310.8,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yeah, those.","index":88,"end_time":313.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":312.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"All of the website changes, including the calendly links, will be done today.","index":89,"end_time":317.92,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":313.28,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":90,"end_time":319.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":318.4,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay, I''ll let you take back over.","index":91,"end_time":322.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":320.72,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Okay, that''s cool though.","index":92,"end_time":324.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":323.01,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Do you know where that lead came from?","index":93,"end_time":326.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":324.97,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"She said, and I talked to Monique yesterday as well.","index":94,"end_time":330.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":326.85,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"The customer said that her.","index":95,"end_time":332.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":330.69,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"She had received some emails.","index":96,"end_time":334.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":332.69,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Okay.","index":97,"end_time":335.73,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":335.17,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"At one point, and then she had reached out to Monique, which Monique says she never talked to her.","index":98,"end_time":341.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":336.29,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"The customer says she did.","index":99,"end_time":343.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":342.37,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So I don''t know if she talked to somebody else or just remembers talking to somebody that a conversation that didn''t happen, I''m not sure.","index":100,"end_time":353.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":344.13,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"But she said she talked to Monique and then went back on and scheduled.","index":101,"end_time":359.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":354.31,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Monique said she never talked to her.","index":102,"end_time":361.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":359.35,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"When she handed off, everything was done.","index":103,"end_time":363.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":361.23,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"There was nothing on her calendar, so I''m not, not real sure.","index":104,"end_time":369.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":363.99,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"But the customer said she did it a week ago and Monique''s been gone for longer than that.","index":105,"end_time":372.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":369.27,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So I''m thinking maybe it was kind of a misunderstanding on the customer''s end of, of what she did.","index":106,"end_time":377.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":373.03,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yeah, but, but yeah, so I, I''ve rescheduled her for today if she ends up accepting.","index":107,"end_time":384.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":378.16,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So.","index":108,"end_time":385.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":384.68,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":109,"end_time":386.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":385.52,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":110,"end_time":387.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":386.56,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Okay, that''s awesome.","index":111,"end_time":390.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":388,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":112,"end_time":390.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":390.12,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So for now, those forms should be working on the site.","index":113,"end_time":394,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":390.88,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"If someone submits it, it''s going to go straight into Zoho, the CRM.","index":114,"end_time":398.4,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":394,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But our developers are going to add the calendar links in today.","index":115,"end_time":402.8,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":399.2,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":116,"end_time":404.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":403.59,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":117,"end_time":405.03,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":404.47,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"All right.","index":118,"end_time":407.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":406.95,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then I also sent over the social media posts yesterday for December.","index":119,"end_time":411.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":407.67,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Once you have a chance to look at those, just let me know if you have any feedback.","index":120,"end_time":415.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":412.71,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''ll review those for you today.","index":121,"end_time":419.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":418.39,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Oh, okay, perfect.","index":122,"end_time":421.19,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":419.79,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, there''s a mix there of like, educational content, so some of the stuff from our podcast episodes, as well as just directly talking about the product and pushing people to book a meeting.","index":123,"end_time":433.73,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":421.59,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":124,"end_time":434.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":434.29,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Great.","index":125,"end_time":438.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":437.73,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then yesterday, I also put together.","index":126,"end_time":441.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":439.01,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"The list of visitors here, which we''ll do on a weekly basis.","index":127,"end_time":446.45,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":442.93,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So a list of accounts or companies that have visited the Agrippon website.","index":128,"end_time":451.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":446.53,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So I put the ones that look the most relevant here at the top.","index":129,"end_time":456.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":453.41,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Also put in the number of views that they''ve had in total.","index":130,"end_time":460.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":457.82,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And we could also see the first pages that they visited and when their latest activity was.","index":131,"end_time":466.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":461.66,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":132,"end_time":467.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":467.42,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"The first one, Memorial Herman, when did they.","index":133,"end_time":475.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":468.46,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"What is their number of views?","index":134,"end_time":476.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":475.06,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And when did they.","index":135,"end_time":477.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":476.26,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Is that just one view?","index":136,"end_time":481.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":480.46,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Last activity was December 8th.","index":137,"end_time":484.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":482.46,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So.","index":138,"end_time":485.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":485.1,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So the number of views is that one column D?","index":139,"end_time":487.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":485.33,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":140,"end_time":488.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":488.05,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So one view since then.","index":141,"end_time":491.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":489.73,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":142,"end_time":492.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":491.73,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":143,"end_time":493.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":492.69,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Can you type that in, please?","index":144,"end_time":494.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":493.25,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":145,"end_time":497.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":496.37,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":146,"end_time":502.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":501.65,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And memorialherman.org but we don''t know these are the ones.","index":147,"end_time":509.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":505.17,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We don''t know who they are.","index":148,"end_time":512.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":509.77,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We just know the company and do.","index":149,"end_time":514.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":512.78,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"In the next ones.","index":150,"end_time":515.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":514.58,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Email clicks.","index":151,"end_time":517.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":516.46,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We do know those people.","index":152,"end_time":518.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":517.34,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Email clicks.","index":153,"end_time":522.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":521.5,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":154,"end_time":522.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":522.26,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We''re still going to put this one in.","index":155,"end_time":524.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":522.58,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, so that''s empty.","index":156,"end_time":525.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":524.54,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":157,"end_time":526.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":526.22,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Content website business.","index":158,"end_time":529.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":527.66,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"This is the one that we do know.","index":159,"end_time":530.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":529.42,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"The specific person this one is, I believe that he submitted a.","index":160,"end_time":536.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":531.74,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"The form on the website.","index":161,"end_time":538.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":537.1,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"He submitted a form.","index":162,"end_time":541.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":540.18,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"He was asking something about E Assist.","index":163,"end_time":544.1,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":542.1,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh.","index":164,"end_time":545.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":544.98,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s.","index":165,"end_time":548.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":547.86,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That''s usually that they are already on the system.","index":166,"end_time":551.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":548.7,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":167,"end_time":552.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":551.94,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":168,"end_time":555.06,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":554.5,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And these are two other contacts.","index":169,"end_time":557.06,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":555.06,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So for these ones we just know their LinkedIn profiles, not their email.","index":170,"end_time":561.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":558.18,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":171,"end_time":564.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":563.78,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Great.","index":172,"end_time":566.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":566.35,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":173,"end_time":567.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":567.07,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Once we add in these email clicks here, then I''ll send this sheet over to you.","index":174,"end_time":571.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":567.43,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":175,"end_time":573.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":571.71,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And that''ll just be a weekly thing, Natalie.","index":176,"end_time":577.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":575.15,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Correct.","index":177,"end_time":578.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":578.11,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":178,"end_time":578.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":578.59,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And what.","index":179,"end_time":579.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":578.95,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"What email you send it over to?","index":180,"end_time":581.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":579.87,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Just directly to our emails?","index":181,"end_time":582.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":581.35,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":182,"end_time":583.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":583.31,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":183,"end_time":584.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":584.03,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"All right.","index":184,"end_time":587.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":587.15,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then like I said.","index":185,"end_time":588.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":588.03,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":186,"end_time":589.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":588.87,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"All the updates for the website will be done today.","index":187,"end_time":591.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":589.11,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We''ll send the pull request.","index":188,"end_time":593.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":591.71,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Jane, then you can get those launched.","index":189,"end_time":596.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":593.07,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":190,"end_time":596.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":596.53,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Please email me when you get the.","index":191,"end_time":598.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":596.93,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That pull request and I''ll launch it and make sure there''s no conflicts.","index":192,"end_time":602.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":598.69,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"If you could.","index":193,"end_time":603.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":602.53,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":194,"end_time":606.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":603.89,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''ll make a note to the developers.","index":195,"end_time":607.57,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":606.05,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":196,"end_time":614.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":614.13,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then just looking at some key stats from our data.","index":197,"end_time":619.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":616.53,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So it looks like our traffic is going up steadily.","index":198,"end_time":623.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":620.72,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Visitors are up 8%.","index":199,"end_time":625.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":623.76,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Page views were up 4%.","index":200,"end_time":627.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":625.52,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"The case study page seems to be growing the Most was up 53% over the last 30 days.","index":201,"end_time":634,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":628.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Contact page is down slightly.","index":202,"end_time":636.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":635.04,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I think that with the new changes that we''re adding with Keenan''s ideas, this might be able to improve because we''re offering different.","index":203,"end_time":645.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":638.32,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Meeting types.","index":204,"end_time":648.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":647.35,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So far we''ve only had the demo requests, but now we''re also including the needs consultation, so we''ll see if that helps.","index":205,"end_time":655.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":648.79,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Direct Traffic is up 9%.","index":206,"end_time":659.19,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":657.19,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So this is people that are repeat visitors or sharing the links with other people.","index":207,"end_time":664.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":659.19,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then ABM traffic is up 53%.","index":208,"end_time":667.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":665.19,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So emails, LinkedIn messages, those are working well.","index":209,"end_time":671.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":667.75,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Keenan, given that these are the numbers, any particular area that you feel like.","index":210,"end_time":679.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":671.76,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We should change in our.","index":211,"end_time":681.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":679.28,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"On our website, for example, Case study.","index":212,"end_time":685,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":683.2,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I remember you talking about it last time we met.","index":213,"end_time":687.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":685,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Is there any particular area that we should change going forward?","index":214,"end_time":690.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":687.599,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Like is it more urgent?","index":215,"end_time":692.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":690.72,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Because if we''re getting more visitors, we might want to.","index":216,"end_time":695.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":693.12,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":217,"end_time":697.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":696.72,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So this is good for me to see.","index":218,"end_time":700.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":697.2,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"This being the first time.","index":219,"end_time":701.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":700.29,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I wouldn''t jump to a change immediately.","index":220,"end_time":703.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":701.53,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I''m going to go back through the case study page.","index":221,"end_time":706.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":704.33,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I''ll make a note of that for me.","index":222,"end_time":708.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":706.45,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"To put on my agenda for this week as well.","index":223,"end_time":712.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":710.01,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And it does sound like the two people that we have set up.","index":224,"end_time":718.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":714.41,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Shane, that email, the one was a connection you had before, right?","index":225,"end_time":722.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":718.33,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"That sent somebody over to you.","index":226,"end_time":724.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":722.45,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":227,"end_time":724.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":724.05,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And the other one.","index":228,"end_time":725.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":724.45,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"The other one came from an email, which is good.","index":229,"end_time":729.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":725.9,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So with me just being in and just starting to see the way the leads are forming and coming together, I would hesitate to jump to an immediate change.","index":230,"end_time":740.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":730.3,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I''d like to see the facelift with the website and then be able to do the facelift on the LinkedIn all when I complete that.","index":231,"end_time":749.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":740.46,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And then that way we can see if any of just the things that we had before, we''re holding us up.","index":232,"end_time":756.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":749.5,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Some of the.","index":233,"end_time":757.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":756.8,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"The old posts and stuff on LinkedIn.","index":234,"end_time":759.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":757.64,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I know I''m a person that browses old stuff and old history and kind of looks at things.","index":235,"end_time":765.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":760.36,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So maybe that was something that was affecting us.","index":236,"end_time":767.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":765.16,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"But I''d like to really just clean things up, get a refresh first and then we''ll kind of revisit that once we''re up and running for a week.","index":237,"end_time":777.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":767.84,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"That sounds good, Keenan.","index":238,"end_time":779.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":778.09,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"What I''m hearing is stay the course.","index":239,"end_time":780.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":779.01,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":240,"end_time":781.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":781.05,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"For now.","index":241,"end_time":781.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":781.49,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Very, very good.","index":242,"end_time":782.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":781.93,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":243,"end_time":783.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":782.89,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":244,"end_time":787.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":786.81,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Those were all of my updates.","index":245,"end_time":788.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":787.37,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Anything else you wanted to go over here, Shane?","index":246,"end_time":792.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":790.73,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"No, I think you were.","index":247,"end_time":794.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":793.69,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So.","index":248,"end_time":795.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":795.13,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"If we have.","index":249,"end_time":797.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":797.05,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Let''s go over how our account is looking.","index":250,"end_time":800.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":797.77,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":251,"end_time":801.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":801.05,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"If you could.","index":252,"end_time":802.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":801.85,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"If you have access to that data, that would be good.","index":253,"end_time":804.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":802.53,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":254,"end_time":805.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":805.31,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And Shane, while she''s getting set up there.","index":255,"end_time":816.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":814.27,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"If we wanted to make it, and I don''t know this yet, I just am proactively thinking if we wanted to adjust the way the.","index":256,"end_time":826.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":818.59,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"The demo works and kind of set something up, you would be the one that does that with me.","index":257,"end_time":830.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":826.59,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Is that right?","index":258,"end_time":831.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":831.12,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I have access to.","index":259,"end_time":833.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":831.76,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So I can help you design the.","index":260,"end_time":836.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":833.28,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Environment that you want to show.","index":261,"end_time":838,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":836.32,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":262,"end_time":838.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":838.4,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":263,"end_time":839.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":838.88,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And.","index":264,"end_time":840.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":840,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And the.","index":265,"end_time":840.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":840.36,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"The reason that I can do that.","index":266,"end_time":842.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":840.8,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Is I believe your account is a billing organization lead.","index":267,"end_time":845.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":842.2,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"It''s like as close to keys of the kingdom as you can have.","index":268,"end_time":849.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":845.8,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Right.","index":269,"end_time":849.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":849.52,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"But you won''t have.","index":270,"end_time":851.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":849.92,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"There''s a roundabout way to do it, but you won''t easily have access to change the.","index":271,"end_time":856.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":852.24,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"The.","index":272,"end_time":859.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":859.03,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"The office side.","index":273,"end_time":860.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":859.35,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And so you''ll say, hey, Shane, I.","index":274,"end_time":861.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":860.43,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Need this ticket created or this resolved or this moved around.","index":275,"end_time":864.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":861.83,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And I''ll be able to do that.","index":276,"end_time":866.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":864.63,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":277,"end_time":867.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":866.47,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":278,"end_time":867.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":867.03,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":279,"end_time":868.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":867.75,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"All right.","index":280,"end_time":871.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":870.79,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So I get this email periodically.","index":281,"end_time":874.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":871.75,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That''s actually what I''m.","index":282,"end_time":875.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":874.19,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I''m referring to.","index":283,"end_time":876.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":875.27,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Mm.","index":284,"end_time":877.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":876.95,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And the email kind of tells me everything.","index":285,"end_time":880.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":878.39,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Oh, the weekly recap email.","index":286,"end_time":883.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":881.99,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It''s not a recap.","index":287,"end_time":885.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":884.65,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"It''s like, where your account is, it says, here''s your points and here''s the points.","index":288,"end_time":888.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":885.77,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But it actually says, like, I owe you points or you have spent more points than we have paid for.","index":289,"end_time":896.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":888.97,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Oh, you''re.","index":290,"end_time":898.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":897.61,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"This information here.","index":291,"end_time":902.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":901.45,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, that might be it.","index":292,"end_time":904.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":903.21,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So we purchased 350.","index":293,"end_time":905.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":904.57,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"You''ve delivered 850.","index":294,"end_time":908.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":906.33,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And so if we''re in debt, how does that work?","index":295,"end_time":912.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":909.62,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, we.","index":296,"end_time":913.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":912.5,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"When Colin and I are working on this, we are.","index":297,"end_time":917.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":914.9,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We''re trying to do a bunch of different activities.","index":298,"end_time":919.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":917.7,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"As you know, over the past few months, we''ve been ramping it up a bit just to try and see what works.","index":299,"end_time":924.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":919.7,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I see.","index":300,"end_time":925.459,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":924.9,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But we''re still.","index":301,"end_time":926.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":925.459,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We''re experimenting to see what works to get us towards our goals.","index":302,"end_time":929.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":926.66,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":303,"end_time":931.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":930.66,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And sometimes because I would.","index":304,"end_time":932.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":931.22,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I would rather be goal oriented than financial oriented.","index":305,"end_time":935.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":932.34,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And you''re aware that we haven''t received.","index":306,"end_time":938.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":936.56,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Much success at this point.","index":307,"end_time":939.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":938.4,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, but this tells me.","index":308,"end_time":941.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":940,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"This communicates that we have to slow down.","index":309,"end_time":943.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":941.68,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And if we have to slow down because.","index":310,"end_time":946,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":944.08,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"You know, we''re doing so much that I can''t keep up with this.","index":311,"end_time":950.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":947.68,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That feels like a little bit of.","index":312,"end_time":952.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":951.6,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"An indentured servant kind of situation.","index":313,"end_time":955.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":952.84,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We''re just going to create this huge debt and then we can''t pay it off.","index":314,"end_time":958.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":955.52,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So is that the case or how does that work?","index":315,"end_time":962.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":959.84,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"There''s.","index":316,"end_time":964.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":963.49,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I mean, there are things that we could slow down on if we feel that they aren''t.","index":317,"end_time":968.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":964.45,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''m not saying I don''t necessarily want to slow down.","index":318,"end_time":972.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":969.17,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I''m not saying that''s my goal.","index":319,"end_time":973.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":972.01,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"What I am saying is, is that.","index":320,"end_time":975.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":973.65,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"If we''re just getting our business in debt, like, oh, we''re just creating this huge debt that we''re gonna have to pay off over, you know, that''s a concern.","index":321,"end_time":985.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":975.21,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":322,"end_time":986.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":985.49,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Let me.","index":323,"end_time":987.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":986.81,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Let me connect with Colin later on and see how it''ll work.","index":324,"end_time":991.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":987.57,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, please do.","index":325,"end_time":993.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":992.44,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":326,"end_time":994.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":994.52,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''ll get back to you, sir.","index":327,"end_time":996.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":994.88,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I appreciate that and I appreciate experimenting.","index":328,"end_time":999.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":996.6,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And we''re going to have to figure something out because we haven''t been successful to this point.","index":329,"end_time":1006.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1001.72,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But this communicates to me that we.","index":330,"end_time":1009.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1006.68,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Just owe you a ton.","index":331,"end_time":1010.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1009.12,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":332,"end_time":1012.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1011.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And is 350.","index":333,"end_time":1014.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1013.32,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Is that a month?","index":334,"end_time":1015.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1014.88,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Natalie, just so I''m understanding this.","index":335,"end_time":1017.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1015.64,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"No, that''s how much a Gripon has purchased in total.","index":336,"end_time":1021.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1018.9,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":337,"end_time":1023.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1022.5,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"The engagement.","index":338,"end_time":1024.1,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1023.14,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Per month you purchase 50 points.","index":339,"end_time":1028.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1026.82,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintj