"Ease Marketing"},{"text":"And there''s.","index":122,"end_time":356.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":356.07,"speaker_name":"Ease Marketing"},{"text":"There''s two different.","index":123,"end_time":357.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":356.67,"speaker_name":"Ease Marketing"},{"text":"Points.","index":124,"end_time":359.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":359.51,"speaker_name":"Ease Marketing"},{"text":"One is, you know, you got.","index":125,"end_time":362.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":360.15,"speaker_name":"Ease Marketing"},{"text":"Here''s.","index":126,"end_time":362.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":362.47,"speaker_name":"Ease Marketing"},{"text":"Here''s kind of how things are and then there''s kind of.","index":127,"end_time":366.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":362.95,"speaker_name":"Ease Marketing"},{"text":"And here''s the complication of that.","index":128,"end_time":369.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":367.27,"speaker_name":"Ease Marketing"},{"text":"And that could be an opportunity for the first little bump both of the tracks have.","index":129,"end_time":374.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":369.75,"speaker_name":"Ease Marketing"},{"text":"The music starts to change up a little bit and then it''s when it''s like, that''s where ease comes in.","index":130,"end_time":379.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":374.31,"speaker_name":"Ease Marketing"},{"text":"That''s when the music pops off.","index":131,"end_time":381.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":379.37,"speaker_name":"Ease Marketing"},{"text":"And I''m really hoping whoever''s mixing can can just kind of try and tie that kind of.","index":132,"end_time":388.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":381.61,"speaker_name":"Ease Marketing"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":133,"end_time":389.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":389.21,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So there''s like a climax once we present the solution.","index":134,"end_time":394.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":390.01,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index"