lestone.  \n    - The timeline aligns with marketing launch preparations needing finalized content early next week.\n\n## **Quality Assurance and Video Output Standards**\n\nThe video quality is generally acceptable, but the team remains attentive to feedback and technical constraints.\n\n- **Colin noted Axel’s concern about video quality, but overall footage appeared fine on the production side** (06:42)  \n    - Ensuring clear visuals is essential for effective user guidance and product demonstration.  \n    - The team will continue monitoring video quality to avoid user confusion or dissatisfaction.  \n    - This quality check supports brand professionalism and user comprehension in final materials.","outline":null,"keywords":["AI agent","resource management dashboard","video animation","script prompts","beta features","video recordings"],"overview":"- **Video Production Update:** 10 initial videos are ready; 95% of animation footage is complete pending AI response scripts.\n\n- **AI Agent Limitations:** Current AI features are in beta, can create resource requests but lack full candidate search capabilities.\n\n- **Script Consistency Needed:** Team to standardize prompt-response pairs to avoid confusion from varied outputs in animations.\n\n- **Documentation as a Guide:** Shared script document will clarify AI responses and desired prompts for consistent production and development.\n\n- **Quality Monitoring:** Team will ensure video quality meets standards to guide users and maintain brand professionalism. \n\n- **Timeline for Finalization:** Hendrik aims to provide updates by Monday, prioritizing quality over rapid completion for marketing launch.","action_items":"\n**Hendrik Pollex**\nAdd comments in the shared document specifying the planned input prompts and expected AI agent responses for the animations (06:26)\nPotentially add a new video to demonstrate correct interaction and outputs of the AI agent (06:42)\nProvide final clarifications and feedback on the video content by Monday at the latest (06:57)\n\n**Colin Costigan**\nReview Hendrik’s comments and additional video once provided, to finalize animation scripts and video production setup (06:42)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"be099788-cae9-4f89-a437-982d3c8f180c","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
